cell topic
  yield question = "What are the three laws of thermodynamics? Explain each in one sentence."

cell answer
  given topic.question
  yield explanation
  ---
  Answer «question» clearly and accurately.
  ---
  check explanation is not empty
  check~ each law is stated correctly with no factual errors
  check~ explanation covers all three laws, not just one or two

cell simplify (stem)
  given answer.explanation
  yield summary
  ---
  Rewrite «explanation» at a 6th-grade reading level. Keep it accurate but use simple words.
  ---
  check summary is not empty
  check~ summary preserves the scientific accuracy of the original
